## Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file based on `.env.example`.

Example:
# ==============================
# Database Configuration
# ==============================

DB_HOST=********
DB_PORT=****
DB_USER=****
DB_PASSWORD=********
DB_NAME=********
DB_TIMEZONE=****/****
DB_SSLMODE=disable


# ==============================
# Application Configuration
# ==============================

APP_PORT=****